message.body: Did you do anything to celebrate the fourth of July?
Okay so far. Family trip to San Francisco. What city are you in?
I met an old friend from high school. Haven't seen her in 20 yrs! What did you do?
Was supposed to go to Fresno to visit my cousin but got sick earlier this week (flu? Head cold?), so canceled the trip and stayed in. Bit of a waste. :-)
